# Example Environment Variables for Archon Agent

# --- AI Provider Configuration ---
# Choose ONE provider and uncomment/set the corresponding variables.
# Ensure your application logic is configured to use the correct variables.

# --- OpenAI ---
# OPENAI_API_KEY="YOUR_OPENAI_API_KEY_HERE"
# OPENAI_MODEL_NAME="gpt-4-turbo-preview" # Example: Or other compatible model like gpt-4o, gpt-3.5-turbo

# --- Anthropic ---
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY="YOUR_ANTHROPIC_API_KEY_HERE"
# ANTHROPIC_MODEL_NAME="claude-3-opus-20240229" # Example: Or other compatible model like claude-3-sonnet-20240229

# --- Google Gemini ---
# GOOGLE_API_KEY="YOUR_GOOGLE_API_KEY_HERE"
# GOOGLE_MODEL_NAME="gemini-1.5-pro-latest" # Example: Or other compatible model like gemini-pro

# --- Generic Settings (Alternative) ---
# If your application uses generic variable names across different providers,
# you might use these instead. Ensure your application logic correctly maps
# these to the specific provider's requirements based on other configurations.
# AI_PROVIDER_API_KEY="YOUR_API_KEY_HERE" # Generic API Key for the selected provider
# AI_MODEL_NAME="PROVIDER_SPECIFIC_MODEL_NAME" # Generic Model Name (replace with actual model for the selected provider)